<pc>」</pc>潛至鎮<pc>，</pc>繕壁壘<pc>，</pc>積粟<pc>，</pc>構高屋偫兵<pc>，</pc>利而嚴<pc>。</pc>遂引師自<placeName>原州</placeName>逾硤石<pc>，</pc>取虜將<measure quantity="1" unit="people">
<num value="1">一</num>人</measure>
