<num value="3">三</num>逃<num value="3">三</num>獲<pc>，</pc>乃轉鬻遠酋<pc>，</pc>酋嚴遇之<pc>，</pc>晝役夜囚<pc>，</pc>沒凡<measure quantity="15" unit="years">
